{"title":"最后一片落叶 （外一首）","authors":["陈广斌"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":2,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"最后一片落叶 （外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈广斌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一页金黄色日历"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被冰凉的秋风撕去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落在松软的草地上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"默默无语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那些绚丽的故事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛已经被候鸟忘记"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它没有枯萎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蜜月虽然已经过去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金黄色的叶脉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"织成生命的小路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流动着透明的记忆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它知道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"芬芳属于花朵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甜蜜属于果实"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它不需要季节的眷顾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只需要一缕忠诚的心语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蘸着秋霜写一封情书"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金黄，如初春黄昏的云霓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赠给曾经热恋的黑土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地将爱的果实"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深深地收藏在心里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"季节鸟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一只候鸟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在落霜的早晨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带着对季节的眷恋与失望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随秋风而去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞走吧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不必为失落啜泣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"命运的风帆已经升起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漫长的旅途中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会抖掉所有的烦恼与忧虑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我能理解你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那双裁风剪雾的翅膀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是为了追索而不是逃避"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从枯萎的极地出发"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不必犹豫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿陌生的风景线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去寻求新的平衡与对比"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}